lib/cookieJar
ExtendedCookieJar
ExtendedCookieJar extends the npm:tough-cookie CookieJar class with the methods below but can otherwise be instantiated as usual, particularly with custom stores, either by extending the tough-cookie Store class yourself or finding an existing package that does so, e.g. "tough-cookie store" search on npm.
